description: This Dart source file defines a data provider class 'DemoData' that supplies static sample data for restaurants and menu items, including methods to access and query this data.

classes.name: DemoData
classes.description: A utility class providing static sample data for restaurants and menu items, with methods for data retrieval.

methods.name: allMenuItems
methods.description: Returns a list of all menu items from the predefined restaurants.

methods.name: restaurantById
methods.description: Returns a restaurant object by its ID, or null if not found.

methods.name: menuItemById
methods.description: Returns a menu item object by its ID, or null if not found.
